===Verb===
'''normalize'''
#To format in a [[standard]]ized manner, to make [[consistent]].
#:''We'll need to '''normalize''' these statements before we can compare them.''
#To make [[normal]], to make [[standard]]
#:''There is little hope that the two countries will '''normalize''' relations; the administration of each country seems to hate each other and would just as soon stay on bad terms.''
#:in [[Math]]/[[Statistics]]:''After we properly '''normalize''' the measurements with respect to age, gender, geography and economic considerations, there remains little evidence of a difference between the two groups.''

